TEXT(&beginproblem);

$a = random(7,9,.01);
$n = random(6,20,1);
$m = $n-2;
$s = random(9,12,.01)+$a;
$i = 1/($a-1)-1/($s+1);
$pre = $i/log(1+$i);

$ans= round($pre*10000)/10000;
&ANS(num_cmp($ans));


TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));

For interest rate \(i\), you are given \(\ddot a_{n+1\rceil}\) = $a and \(\ddot s_{n-1\rceil}\) = $s.  Find \(\overline {s}_{1\rceil}\).
$BR
$BR
\(\overline {s}_{1\rceil}\) = \{ans_rule(20)\}?
$BR

EOT


